---
---
<section data-test="cta-section" style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);background:var(--color-surface);">
  <div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-size:0.75rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Open Source</h2>
    <h3 style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--color-text);max-width:640px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      RootSpec is open source and works with any stack, any team, any AI tooling.
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.7;max-width:560px;margin-bottom:2rem;">
      The framework, all four skills, and the complete spec for this site are available on GitHub. Four commands from a seed to a deployed, tested site.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;align-items:center;">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:500;padding:0.65rem 1.25rem;background:var(--color-accent);color:#fff;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;transition:opacity 150ms ease-out;"
      >
        View on GitHub →
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos/tree/main/greenfield"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;"
      >
        See this demo's source
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
